#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn36.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn36.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 36 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 36 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Aṭṭhasatapariyāyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Explanation of the Hundred and Eight "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn36.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Ñāṇasutta "
msgstr "25. Knowledge "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.234, sc1
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.1"
msgid "“‘Imā vedanā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi. "
msgstr "“‘These are the feelings.’ Such was the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me regarding teachings not learned before from another. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.2"
msgid "‘Ayaṃ vedanāsamudayo’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi … pe … āloko udapādi. "
msgstr "‘This is the origin of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.3"
msgid "‘Ayaṃ vedanāsamudayagāminī paṭipadā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi … pe … "
msgstr "‘This is the practice that leads to the origin of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.4"
msgid "‘ayaṃ vedanānirodho’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi … pe … "
msgstr "‘This is the cessation of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.5"
msgid "‘ayaṃ vedanānirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi … pe … "
msgstr "‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.6"
msgid "‘ayaṃ vedanāya assādo’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu … pe … "
msgstr "‘This is the gratification of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.7"
msgid "‘ayaṃ vedanāya ādīnavo’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu … pe … "
msgstr "‘This is the drawback of feeling.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.8"
msgid "‘idaṃ kho nissaraṇan’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādī”ti. "
msgstr "‘This is the escape from feeling.’ Such was the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me regarding teachings not learned before from another.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn36.25:1.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
